    "body": "https://github.com/facebook/react-native/issues/28774\r\n\r\nThere is no way to properly fix this bug at the moment. We can implement a kind of fix mentioned in the issue above, but it will rather cause flickering UI.  \r\n\r\nAnother option is to allow user to type more than 600 chars and then disable `send` button and somehow emphasise that limit has been exceeded. That might cause worse UX, but at least it will be more predictable. :) Also this is only needed for iOS version.\r\n\r\n ",
